      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spinach has wilted, add <strong>half</strong> your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>Greek cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
