    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pasta is cooked, add it to the pan with the sauce</p><p>Stir everything together and cook for 1-2 min further or until the sauce begins to stick to the pasta – this is your <strong>Greek cheese, chorizo & spinach tortiglioni</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if the sauce is looking a little thick!</p>",
